strategy_rules: Prioritize micro-cap tokens (<100k) - they had the highest win rate among all market cap categories.
Avoid tokens with extreme volume spikes (vol_extreme_spike > 3x) as they had a high loss rate, but consider moderate volume spikes (e.g., 0.82x and 2.14x) which were present in some winning trades
Require age between 6-24h - trades in this age range had the highest win rate (46.2%) among all age categories.
Prioritize tokens with buy ratio > 1.5, but also consider trades with lower buy ratios (e.g., 1.1 and 1.23) which were present in some winning trades, with a focus on buy ratios above 1.0
Avoid tokens with high 1h change at entry (> 20%) and extreme volume spikes, as they had lower win rates and higher losses, but consider trades with lower 1h change and moderate volume spikes
Prioritize tokens with pressure_balanced, as they had a higher average ROI (+592.9%) and win rate (37.5%)
Favor tokens with normal volume (vol_normal), as they had a higher average ROI (+342.8%) and win rate (35.7%)

Consider tokens with pressure_heavy_buying, as they had a high average ROI (+604.2%) and a moderate win rate (42.9%), but prioritize pressure_balanced tokens due to their higher win rate and average ROI
Prioritize tokens with age between 1-6h due to their high average ROI (+1198.5%) and moderate win rate (25.0%)
Favor tokens with normal volume (vol_normal) due to their higher average ROI (+536.4%) and win rate (35.3%) compared to other volume categories
avoid_conditions: AVOID tokens already pumped >100% in 1h (lost -29.8% on テディベア (TEDDY))
AVOID tokens with liq/MC ratio <5% (thin liquidity trap, lost on ORGAZM)
AVOID tokens with sell pressure (ratio <1.0) (lost -27.9% on Punch’s Father)
AVOID tokens with sell pressure (ratio <1.0) (lost -19.2% on Punch’s Father)
AVOID tokens with sell pressure (ratio <1.0) (lost -14.4% on Punch’s Father)
Prioritize tokens with age between 6-24 hours
Consider tokens with high buy pressure and moderate volume
